description: The Cluck Truck is cooking up something fantastic, just for you! Serving up southern fried comfort food you're sure to love, Cluck is owned and operated by Alabama's own Chef Rachael Tremaine, who's bringing all her favorite recipes to the streets of Colorado. If you're looking for the best chicken fingers, hand cut fries, deep fried mac & cheese, and more, then this is the food truck for you!
name: The Cluck Truck
